1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,800
Why do peacocks flaunt those stunning tails?

2
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:08,800
It all comes down to sexual selection—a process where mates are chosen based on traits.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,200
But it's not just about beauty.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:13,600
Those tails signal health and vitality.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:17,200
Research shows females prefer males with larger, brighter tails.

6
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,800
More tail, more mates!

7
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:21,600
But remember, not every trait guarantees success.

8
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:22,400
Nature's complex!

9
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:24,000
Like what you learned?

10
